.section *refid='caution' caution
.*
.ix 'caution'
.ix 'Block' 'caution'
.ix 'Generated text' 'caution'
.ix 'Notices' 'caution'
.tag begin
.tdesc
Displays a locale-specific cautionary message ("Caution: " in the en_US locale)
followed on the next line by the contents enclosed by the caution tag block.
.tclose ecaution
.tattrbs
.tattr text='message'
Use 'message' instead of 'CAUTION: ' as the introductory text.
.tattrend
.tclass Block
.tcont Text, Formatting, In-line, Block (except acviewport, fn, h1-h6), List-block
.tseealso
:HDREF refid='note'., :HDREF refid='nt'., :HDREF refid='warning'.
.tag end

